<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>طَبَقَاتُ الرُّوَاةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٩٥٠ - وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الطَّبَقَاتُ»</span> لِلرُّوَاةِ تُعْرَفُ … بِالسِّنِّ وَالْأَخْذِ، وَقَدْ تَخْتَلِفُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٩٥١ - فَالصَّاحِبُونَ بِاعْتِبَارِ الصُّحْبَهْ … طَبَقَةٌ، وَفَوْقَ عَشْرٍ رُتْبَهْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٩٥٢ -<span style="color:#006d98"> وَمِنْ مُفَادِ النَّوْعِ:</span> أَنْ يُفَصَّلَا … عِنْدَ اتِّفَاقِ الِاسْمِ وَالَّذِي تَلَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>• • •<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>